data.description: Beautiful and spacious remodeled home with an open concept, and a scenic country setting on 4+ acres. The four bedrooms and three full baths add to the appeal, providing comfort and functionality. The back deck is a great spot to relax and take in the open country views. The large kitchen is likely a fantastic space for cooking and entertaining. Additionally, being just minutes away from downtown South Haven and Lake Michigan offers convenient access to amenities and the beach. It's a wonderful place to move and enjoy a peaceful country lifestyle. Preferred lender offers discounted rate for this listing.
